quran[11{c,v,t}:
19,1,Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-'Ayyyn-Saaad
19,2,( yeh ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani ka bayan ( hai jo is ne ) apne bande zikria par ( ki thi )
19,3,jab unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ko dubi aawaz se puraka
19,4,( aur ) kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar meri haddiyan burhapay ke sabab kamzor hogayi hain aur sir ( hai ke ) burhapay ( ki wajah se ) shola maarny laga hai aur ae mere perwar-digaar mein tujh se maang kar kabhi mahroom nahi raha
19,5,aur mein apne baad apne bhai bundon se darta hon aur meri biwi banjh hai to mujhe apne paas se aik waris ataa farma
19,6,jo meri aur aulaad Yaqoob ki meeras ka maalik ho. aur ( ae ) mere perwar-digaar is ko khush atwaar banaiyo
19,7,ae zikria hum tum ko aik larke ki basharat dete hain jis ka naam yahya hai. is se pehlay hum ne is naam ka koi shakhs peda nahikiya
19,8,unhon ne kaha perwar-digaar mere haan kis terhan larka hoga. jis haal mein meri biwi banjh hai aur mein burhapay ki intahaa ko poanch gaya hon
19,9,hukum howa ke isi terhan ( hoga ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne farmaya hai ke mujhe yeh aasaan hai aur mein pehlay tum ko bhi to peda krchka hon aur tum kuch cheez nah they
19,10,kaha ke perwar-digaar mere liye koi nishani muqarrar farma. farmaya nishani yeh hai ke tum sahih وسالم ho kar teen ( raat din ) logon se baat nah krsko ge
19,11,phir woh ( ibadat ke ) hujray se nikal kar apni qoum ke paas aeye to un se isharay se kaha ke subah vsham ( khuda ko ) yaad karte raho
